WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.100 --> 00:00:02.366
Ruolan, you beg for shame for me

2
00:00:02.366 --> 00:00:04.666
To make you change your mind

3
00:00:04.933 --> 00:00:07.166
He persisted for ten years

4
00:00:07.666 --> 00:00:09.200
Bitter for ten years

5
00:00:09.466 --> 00:00:11.400
I have been waiting for you for ten years

6
00:00:11.400 --> 00:00:12.800
Finally got you back

7
00:00:12.800 --> 00:00:14.666
What did you do when you got back?

8
00:00:14.733 --> 00:00:16.900
You come back and beat him, scold him, even insult him

9
00:00:16.900 --> 00:00:17.700
and

10
00:00:17.700 --> 00:00:20.300
When he was about to prove his innocence

11
00:00:20.300 --> 00:00:22.066
You smashed me and gave up

12
00:00:22.066 --> 00:00:25.366
You deserve to be his mother in this life, right?

13
00:00:25.366 --> 00:00:26.600
And you know what?

14
00:00:26.600 --> 00:00:29.433
It's your blood that runs through his bones

15
00:00:29.500 --> 00:00:31.300
Why are you so poisonous?

16
00:00:31.400 --> 00:00:33.466
Why did you do this to him?

17
00:00:33.566 --> 00:00:35.200
Because you are poor

18
00:00:35.266 --> 00:00:38.433
Because you are all a bunch of lowly social underclass

19
00:00:38.466 --> 00:00:40.766
Because it is impossible for Zhao Ruolan to conceive at all

20
00:00:40.766 --> 00:00:44.266
Champion, my husband helps the nobles of the Three Kingdoms

21
00:00:44.266 --> 00:00:45.666
Rich and powerful

22
00:00:45.866 --> 00:00:48.100
My son was born into a wealthy family

23
00:00:48.133 --> 00:00:50.266
And this year's Olympic champion

24
00:00:50.266 --> 00:00:51.700
I am seven poor and rich

25
00:00:51.700 --> 00:00:52.966
Mother poor child

26
00:00:52.966 --> 00:00:54.733
Enjoying endless glory and wealth

27
00:00:54.733 --> 00:00:58.766
And you, Zhao Ruolan, will only bring me endless shame

